query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('algebraic-geometry',
'complex-analysis')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math',
'physics')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Cleanup',
'Deputy',
'Famous Question',
'Guru',
'Inquisitive',
'Peer Pressure',
'Pundit',
'Reviewer',
'Self-Learner',
'Strunk & White',
'Talkative',
'Vox Populi')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
